  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🪐 <i>VOID PULSE</i> — A strange vibration echoes through the void</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An unknown signal pulses across the edges of deep space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After a long break of inactivité, <strong>VOID PULSE</strong> is now a game in active development — a modular experience built to evolve over time. Exploration, tension, and emergence in a minimalist but expandable framework.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drive, shoot.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dodge, destroy!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >** READ EARLY ACCESS SECTION BEFORE BUYING**</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >** THIS IS A VERY EARLY VERSION THE GAME, MANY THINGS WILL COME TO CHANGE AND EVOLVE**</p>",
